graphql.query:
query($userId: ID!) {
    getUser(_id: $userId){
        firstName
        lastName
        middleName
        email
        kind
        companyName
        provider {
            _id
            firstName
            lastName
            middleName
            phoneNumber
            emailAddresses
            credentials
            active
            identifiers {
                id
                idType
            }
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
        _id
    }
}
